snippet.title: Crash Bandicoot Flash Game Complete Walkthrough
snippet.description:
CHEAT - DESCRIPTION
HUDABEGA - Plays a diff sound.
No5SHINE - Obtain all gems
GotZOOKA - Sets power #4 to have - use 'S' to pull out
FruitUzi - Sets power #5 to have
CAKEWALK - Sets power #8 to have
OLYMPICS - sets power #10 to have
HALELUYA - adds 1 life (if lives are less than 98)
AutoLife - adds 10 lives (if lives are less than 89)
OLYMPICS lets you dash by holding D while running.
